    "Name": "Katydid WCV",
    "Details": "Created as a support vehicle for battlemech lances, the Katydid Wheeled Combat Vehicle is an 80 ton fire support vehicle. Powered by a 300 rated fusion engine, the Katydid is capable of reaching a speed of 60kph while carrying 11 tons of ferro-fibrous armor. Mounted in the turret is an Artemis IV enhanced LRM-15 and a RAC/5, with a pair of Medium Pulse Lasers providing backup at closer ranges.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: None.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 4/6 hexes / 120/180 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       245     40\n<b>Left</b>         195     40\n<b>Right</b>       195     40\n<b>Rear</b>        155     40\n<b>Turret</b>      195     40\n\n<b>Total</b>      985    200</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Long</color>",
